@baseUrl = https://coders-camp-schronisko.herokuapp.com/api
 
### Get all animals
GET {{baseUrl}}/animals

### Get animal
GET {{baseUrl}}/animals/1

### Register user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

