### Activate user
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/activate/c6845061-f7d8-4cd0-b659-785cdfbcdaeb

### Login user
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "mail": "elo@elo.elo",
